Class MusicPlayerView.SongTile

java.lang.Object

view.MusicPlayerView.SongTile
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
Enclosing class:
MusicPlayerView
private class MusicPlayerView.SongTile extends javafx.scene.layout.BorderPane
This class encapsulates an entire Song object and displays it visually. It highlights the song when hovered over, highlights it while it is playing, and is able to play it when clicking the playButton that is revealed when SongTile is hovered over with the mouse.
Author:
Leighanna/Jackson
